---
title: Cacio e Pepe with charred courgette and marinated tomatoes
description: Cacio e pepe—literally translated as cheese and pepper—is a pasta dish that hails from the Italian city of Rome. The beauty of this recipe is the amazing flavours created using simple but standout ingredients.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R08_W08_IE_IECFQVV13682-2_Main_high-bcdb7c2a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/cacio-e-pepe-638f175e2d630dceaa85ac7a-3ba4363e.pdf
